casebody.data:
Wednesday, October 3, 2001

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

01-1728. State ex rel. Gracyzk v. Lorain Cty. Bd. of Elections.

This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus regarding an expedited election matter. Upon consideration of relator’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
